{{version030}}
Here is a list of all the '''bad mutations''' you can ''acquire''. Although some may have situational uses, they are at best mixed blessings. Regardless, "bad mutation" is a technical term used by the game, not a qualitative judgement. Any of these can be acquired through any [[mutation#Bad_mutations|source of bad mutations]].

